Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.40,Pop,,0,0,0,,Anyone can visit. You
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:02.79,Pop,,0,0,0,,can swim where {\c&H00FFFF&}Grant{\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:04.13,Pop,,0,0,0,,walked and surf where
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:05.22,Pop,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Garfield{\c&HFFFFFF&} was carried to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:06.22,Pop,,0,0,0,,die. On the grounds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:07.22,Pop,,0,0,0,,of the Church of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:08.15,Pop,,0,0,0,,the Pres idents there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.12,Pop,,0,0,0,,is a small tea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:10.42,Pop,,0,0,0,,house. It was built
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.72,Pop,,0,0,0,,from the actual {\c&H00FFFF&}railroad{\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.20,Pop,,0,0,0,,ties that volunteers laid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.55,Pop,,0,0,0,,through the night to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:15.91,Pop,,0,0,0,,bring a dying president
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.13,Pop,,0,0,0,,to the sea. One
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:18.16,Pop,,0,0,0,,of the original iron
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.74,Pop,,0,0,0,,rails serves as its
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.32,Pop,,0,0,0,,ridge pole, {\c&H00FFFF&}seven{\c&HFFFFFF&} presidents,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:23.66,Pop,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}four{\c&HFFFFFF&} undeniable, {\c&H00FFFF&}three{\c&HFFFFFF&} debatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:25.17,Pop,,0,0,0,,But the stories they
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.68,Pop,,0,0,0,,left behind of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:28.12,Pop,,0,0,0,,of tragedy, of a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:29.49,Pop,,0,0,0,,community pushing a train
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:30.84,Pop,,0,0,0,,car by hand, those
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.19,Pop,,0,0,0,,are real. This is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:33.33,Pop,,0,0,0,,the first of {\c&H00FFFF&}five{\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:34.70,Pop,,0,0,0,,videos. Next, Grant's poker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:36.17,Pop,,0,0,0,,games and financial ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:37.80,Pop,,0,0,0,,Then the full {\c&H00FFFF&}Garfield{\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.66,Pop,,0,0,0,,story, 79 days, then
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:41.46,Pop,,0,0,0,,Wilson's broken promise and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:43.02,Pop,,0,0,0,,the resort itself ,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.23,Pop,,0,0,0,,the hotels, the gamblers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:46.41,Pop,,0,0,0,,and the fire. Subscribe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:48.59,Pop,,0,0,0,,so you do not
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:49.68,Pop,,0,0,0,,miss them.
